des:
FOR DUCKS FANS! Let's say you're in the kitchen, or your bedroom, and you want to see what's happening with your Ducks without pulling out your phone.

Just say, Alexa, open the Ducks Latest Tweet!

You can also activate the goal horn to brighten up your day!

Enjoy,

Kelly Johns
